      "descriptionEn": "5-step cognitive dissonance detection framework, from value auditing to behavior pairing, finding cracks between claimed beliefs and actual behavior",
      "scenarioEn": "Personal growth seekers, managers, team members wanting to improve self-awareness, eliminate internal friction, and align behavior with values",
