      "descriptionEn": "7-round ultimate subtraction framework, from packaging stripping to core extraction, helping you find the irreducible essence in projects, business, or life",
      "scenarioEn": "Strategic decision-makers, product managers, founders, minimalists needing to find essence in complexity and stop wasting resources on irrelevant things",
      "problemFocus": "被包装、仪式和惯性绑架，在99%的非本质事物上消耗资源，核心目标反而被稀释",
