      "descriptionEn": "Six workflow efficiency amplifiers: Plan+Auto-accept, multi-terminal parallel, restrained MCP usage, feedback loop, Ralph overnight loop, Auto Memory self-growth",
      "scenarioEn": "Upgrade from personal single-thread usage to multi-concurrent, auto-verification, self-evolving engineering workflow",
      "problemFocus": "单线程使用Claude Code效率受限，不知道如何叠加多种技术实现指数级效率提升",
